IU KHON CHUNG HP NG CUNG CP V S DNG DCH V
(nh km hp ng cung cp dch v s..k ngy)
- Cn c B Lut Dn s; Lut Vin thng; Lut Bo v Quyn li Ngi tiu dng; Lut Giao dch in t;
- Cn c Ngh nh s 25/2011/N-CP ngy 06/04/2011, c sa i, b sung bi Ngh nh s 81/2016/N-CP
ngy 01/07/2016; Ngh nh s 99/2011/N-CP ngy 27/10/2011; Ngh nh s 72/2013/N-CP ngy
15/07/2013; Ngh nh s 06/2016/N-CP ngy 18/01/2016;
- Cn c Thng t s 24/2016/TT-BTTTT ngy 15/11/2016; Thng t s 39/2016/TT-BTTTT ngy 26/12/2016;
Thng t 16/2018/TT-BTTTT ngy 05/12/2018.
iu khon chung nh nu chi tit di y, l phn khng tch ri ca Hp ng cung cp Dch v (sau y
gi tt l Hp ng), c k kt gia Khch hng-Bn s dng Dch v (sau y gi tt l Bn A) v Cng ty
C phn Cng ngh QI-Bn cung cp Dch v (sau y gi tt l Bn B)
iu 1: i tng ca Hp ng:
1.1 i tng ca Hp ng l dch v truy nhp
Internet (khng c cc dch v gi tr gia tng i km)
(sau y gi tt l Dch v).
1.2 a im cung cp Dch v: ti a ch hp php ca
Bn A, do Bn A yu cu cung cp Dch v ti .
iu 2: M t, cht lng v gi cc Dch v:
M t, cht lng dch v c din gii v cng b cng
khai ti cc im giao dch ca Bn B v trn website
ca Bn B ti ng dn: http://qi.com.vn. m bo cht
lng dch v ng nh cam kt vi Bn A v Bn B
cng b.
Gi dch v c nim yt trn website http://qi.com.vn,
c thng bo cho Khch hng v c Hai bn thng
nht khi k kt Hp ng.
iu 3: Thi hn Hp ng:
Thi hn Hp ng l 01 (mt) nm (Thi hn). Khi
thi hn ca Hp ng kt thc, nu trong vng 30 (ba
mi) ngy trc khi ht hn m cc Bn khng c tha
thun khc bng vn bn chnh thc th Hp ng c
t ng gia hn thm 01 (mt) nm v khng hn ch s
ln t ng gia hn.
iu 4: Quyn v ngha v ca Bn A:
4.1 Quyn ca Bn A: c quyn yu cu Bn B:
a. Cung cp thng tin lin quan n vic s dng Dch
v.
b. Cung cp Dch v theo cht lng v gi cc nu
ti iu 2.
c. Bn A c quyn khiu ni v gi cc, cht lng Dch
v; c hon tr gi cc v bi thng thit hi trc
tip do li ca Bn B hoc i l ca Bn B gy ra.
d. Bn A c quyn m bo b mt cc thng tin ring
c ghi trong Hp ng.
e. Bn A c quyn n phng chm dt thc hin Hp
ng ti bt k thi im no sau khi thng bo bng vn
bn cho Bn B v Bn B nhn c thng bo. Trong
trng hp Bn A n phng chm dt thc hin Hp
ng, Bn A ch phi thanh ton cc ph, l ph (nu c)
cho phn Dch v m mnh s dng.
f. Bn A c quyn t chi s dng mt phn hoc ton
b dch v c cung cp nh nu ti Hp ng ny.
g. Cc quyn khc theo quy nh hin hnh ca php lut
Vit Nam.
4.2 Ngha v ca Bn A:
a. S dng Dch v theo ng cc quy nh ca php lut
Vit Nam. Bn A cam kt hon ton chu trch nhim
trc php lut Vit Nam nu vi phm php lut Vit
Nam khi s dng Dch v.
b. Thanh ton y , ng hn cc ph dch v s
dng Dch v theo Hp ng.
c. Bi thng thit hi do li ca mnh gy ra cho Bn B
hoc i l ca Bn B.
d. Hon ton t chu trch nhim trc php lut Vit
Nam v ni dung thng tin truyn, a, lu tr trn khng
gian mng.
e. Khng c li dng c s h tng ca Bn B kinh
doanh li dch v tng t Dch v do Bn B ang cung
cp cho Bn A.
f. Thng bo bng vn bn cho Bn B v phi hp vi
Bn B thc hin cc th tc cn thit, khi: chuyn quyn
s dng Dch v; thay i thng tin cung cp v s dng
Dch v; thay i hnh thc thanh ton, hnh thc nhn
thng bo cc, bn k chi tit thanh ton cc, hoc
thng bo chm dt Hp ng.
g. Bo v v chu trch nhim v mt khu, kha mt
khu, thit b u cui s dng Dch v.
h. Trng hp Bn A vi phm cam kt cc chng trnh
khuyn mi hoc u i do Bn B a ra th Bn A phi
hon tr cho Bn B ton b gi tr khuyn mi hoc u
i nhn v phi hon tr thit b u cui c
Bn B trang b (nu c).
i. Cc ngha v khc theo quy nh hin hnh ca php
lut Vit Nam.
iu 5: Quyn v ngha v ca Bn B:
5.1 Quyn ca Bn B:
a. c quyn yu cu Bn A thc hin ng cc ni
dung ca Hp ng v Tha thun khc (nu c).
b. c quyn yu cu Bn A cung cp thng tin ring
cn thit lin quan n vic cung cp Dch v.
c. c quyn yu cu Bn A thanh ton y , ng
hn gi cc s dng Dch v v cc khon ph, l ph
ghi trong Hp ng.
d. c quyn tm ngng cung cp Dch v hoc chm
dt Hp ng theo quy nh ti iu 7 v iu 8 ca
iu khon chung ny.
e. c quyn thc hin cc quyn khc theo quy nh
hin hnh ca php lut Vit Nam
5.2 Ngha v ca Bn B:
a. Bn B phi thng xuyn o kim cht lng Dch v
m mnh cung cp, m bo cht lng Dch v nh
cam kt vi Bn A v doanh nghip cng b.
b. m bo b mt thng tin ring ca Bn A, ch c
chuyn giao thng tin cho bn th ba khi c c s ng
ca Bn A, tr cc trng hp khc theo quy nh ca
php lut Vit Nam.
c. Trng hp Bn A thng bo s c hoc khiu ni v
cht lng Dch v, Bn B phi kp thi kim tra, gii
quyt khiu ni ca Bn A theo thi hn quy nh ca
php lut.
d. Cung cp cho Bn A ha n cc ph s dng Dch
v, bn k chi tit cc Dch v theo ng quy nh php
lut hin hnh.
e. Thc hin cc yu cu hp php ca Bn A v chuyn
quyn s dng Dch v, thay i thng tin cung cp v
s dng Dch v.
f. Khi phc Dch v sau khi Bn A hon thnh cc
ngha v ca mnh i vi trng hp b tm ngng cung
cp Dch v theo quy nh ca iu 7 trong iu khon
chung ny.
g. Khng c t chi giao kt Hp ng hoc n
phng chm dt Hp ng vi Bn A, tr cc trng
hp c quy nh ti Lut vin thng (iu 26) v
khon 8.2 iu 8 iu khon chung ny.
h. Khng c n phng chm dt thc hin Hp
ng, ngng cung cp Dch v m khng c l do chnh
ng. Trng hp cn sa cha, bo tr hoc v l do no
khc bt buc phi ngng cung cp Dch v, Bn B phi
thng bo trc cho Bn A chm nht l 3 (ba) ngy lm
vic trc ngy dng cung cp Dch v;
i. Thng bo cho Bn A v vic ngng cung cp Dch v
t nht 30 (ba mi) ngy trc khi chnh thc ngng
kinh doanh loi hnh dch v ang cung cp cho bn A.
k. Tr trng hp cc Bn c tha thun khc, khng
c yu cu Bn A thanh ton bt k khon tin no
trc khi Dch v c cung cp n Bn A.
l. Cc ngha v khc theo quy nh hin hnh ca php
lut Vit Nam.
iu 6: Thanh ton cc ph:
6.1 Hnh thc Bn A thanh ton vi Bn B: Theo tho
thun trong Hp ng.
6.2 Bn B gi Thng bo cc, Ha n cc s dng
hng thng cho Bn A theo tha thun ca hai bn trong
Hp ng.
6.3 Bn A c trch nhim thanh ton cho Bn B y
cc khon cc ph theo Thng bo cc nhn t Bn
B trc ngy 26 hng thng ca thng pht sinh cc.
iu 7: Tm ngng cung cp Dch v:
7.1 Trong trng hp Bn A c nhu cu tm ngng s
dng Dch v, Bn A phi c vn bn yu cu Bn B gii
quyt, thc hin cc th tc, thanh ton ht cc khon
cc phi tr tnh n thi im tm ngng (nu c) theo
quy nh php lut hin hnh.
7.2 Bn B c quyn n phng tm ngng cung cp
Dch v nu xy ra mt trong cc trng hp di y:
a. Bn A khng thc hin ng ngha v c quy nh
ti im b khon 4.2 iu 4 hoc khon 6.3 iu 6 ca
iu khon chung ny hoc vi phm cc tha thun
khc ca hai Bn (nu c).
b. Bn A cung cp cc thng tin khng chnh xc lin
quan n Hp ng, s dng Dch v khng ng quy
nh ca php lut Vit Nam.
c. Thit b u cui, mng ni b, dy thu bao ca Bn
A khng m bo cc ch tiu cht lng quy nh,
nh hng n cht lng h tng mng li Bn B.
d. Bn B t chc nng cp, tu b, sa cha h tng mng
li theo k hoch hoc do cc nguyn nhn bt kh
khng xy ra c bn B cng khai ti website ca Bn
B theo ng dn: http://qi.com.vn v theo thng bo
trc cho Bn A.
e. Theo yu cu ca c quan Nh nc c thm quyn.
f. Trong nhng trng hp trn, Bn B c trch nhim
thng bo trc cho Bn A chm nht l 3 (ba) ngy lm
vic trc ngy ngng cung cp Dch v. i vi nhng
trng hp khn cp, Bn B c ngha v thng bo cho
Bn A trong vng 24 gi k t khi tm ngng cung cp
Dch v;
iu 8: Chm dt Hp ng:
8.1 Bn A c quyn chm dt Hp ng khi khng c
nhu cu tip tc s dng Dch v, trong trng hp ny
Bn A phi n c s giao dch ca Bn B thc hin cc
th tc chm dt Hp ng. Hp ng chnh thc chm
dt hiu lc, k t khi Bn A v Bn B tha thun trong
ni dung Bin bn chm dt Hp ng. Bn A c trch
nhim thanh ton phn cc, ph s dng v c
nhn li khon cc, ph tr trc (nu c).
8.2 Bn B c quyn n phng chm dt Hp ng
trong cc trng hp sau:
a. Kt thc thi gian tm ngng cung cp Dch v theo
quy nh ti khon 7.1 iu 7 iu khon chung ny
m Bn A khng c yu cu tip tc s dng Dch v.
b. Sau 90 ngy k t ngy Bn A b tm ngng cung cp
Dch v theo quy nh ti im a, b, c khon 7.2 iu 7
m Bn A vn khng thc hin cc ngha v ca mnh
nh iu khon chung v Hp ng quy nh.
c. Bn A c hnh vi lm nh hng n an ton khng
gian mng v an ninh thng tin hoc c hnh vi vi phm
khc trong vic s dng Dch v m hnh vi c quy
nh, m t ti cc vn bn php lut Vit Nam.
d. C yu cu ca c quan Nh nc c thm quyn.
f. Trong nhng trng hp trn, Bn B c trch nhim
thng bo trc cho Bn A chm nht l ba (03) ngy
lm vic trc ngy chm dt cung cp Dch v. i vi
nhng trng hp khn cp hai Bn thng nht p dng
cc qui nh v tm ngng cung cp dch v.
iu 9: Gii quyt tranh chp v bi thng thit hi:
Mi tranh chp lin quan n Hp ng s c gii
quyt thng qua thng lng gia cc Bn. Nu tranh
chp khng th gii quyt thng qua thng lng, cc
Bn c quyn yu cu ta n c thm quyn gii quyt
theo quy nh ca php lut Vit Nam.
iu 10: iu khon cui cng:
10.1 Trong qu trnh k kt v thc hin Hp ng, cc
Bn c th c nhng Tha thun khc nhng khng c
tri vi iu khon chung ny v m bo tun th theo
quy nh php lut Vit Nam hin hnh.
10.2 i vi cc vn pht sinh khng c ghi trong
iu khon chung v Hp ng th p dng theo php
lut Vit Nam hin hnh.
10.3 Nu cc vn bn php lut nu trong phn Cn c
c sa i, b sung, hy b th cc quy nh lin quan
trong iu khon chung cng c thay i tng
ng./.
